The City of Tshwane has been naming, shaming and disconnecting electricity defaulters. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The City of Joburg is embarking on Operation Buya Mthetho. It hopes to recoup about R38-billion in unpaid bills But Ian Ferguson, who helps people with their bills, says the city should first sort out its billing crisis. READ: Joburg mayor vows to fix billing crisis He says numerous claims and complaints are still open and unresolved.